    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know they love me, but i see the way their faces fall when they walk into my room. i see them sighing when they have to help me with the small things. it just feels selfish to keep dragging them through this. it’s like... wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if i just wasn't an issue to deal with anymore? if i just stopped being a problem?",
